column5: Yes I have used them great lead acid 31 deep cycle battery for the electric motor highly recommend for the price.

I was going to buy two Interstate batteries, but only one was available. Went to the local auto parts store and they had the Aqua Edge. When he rang me up, I thought he only charged me for one, but he said that was the cost...both for under $140. Worth a shot anyway.
Just bought two of these. Not what I wanted but needed now so I will see how they do. My interstate and duracell batteries have only got two years anyways so why not.
